HEALTHCARE COMPLIANCE NOTICE:

This software is intended for demonstration purposes only. Before using this
software with real patient data or in a production healthcare environment,
ensure compliance with:

- HIPAA (Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act)
- HITECH (Health Information Technology for Economic and Clinical Health Act)
- State and local healthcare privacy regulations
- Applicable international healthcare data protection laws

The authors and contributors of this software are not responsible for any
compliance violations or data breaches that may occur from the use of this
software in healthcare environments.
